children.subject: <md>Not sure about 285 or 106A but the last project of 162 can be quite time consuming (file system). It is much harder than the other two 162 projects imo.</md>

I am in 106a rn, but I just finished 162. I agree that project 3 is the most time consuming and that class is honestly just a ludicrous amount of work. From what I have heard about 106a, the class is mediumish workload until the project, at which point the workload is sorta high. I don't really know what 285 is, but the combination of 106a and 162 is already kinda high workload towards the end.
